{"tid":1916490,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［重要］信報：何妖想提修正案 削減港台撥款","createTime":"2020-03-09T01:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T03:32:18.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"087d7fa3bc1a33a2ad95603bc2472eab80e4404d","tid":1916490,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:55:56.000Z","msg":"香港電台《頭條新聞》最近再次成為政治風眼，政界消息傳出，立法會議員何君堯打算提出修訂案，要求削減作為港台總編輯的廣播處長梁家榮薪酬，以及縮減製作《頭條新聞》的公共事務組撥款。據了解，何君堯事前未與其他建制議員磋商，不少人得悉有關計劃後都大感不滿，認為何君堯有擺他們上枱之嫌⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2397487\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2397487&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caMzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=c5f45f6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2397487</a><br />\n<br />\n內文大概：<br />\n保皇想口頭反抗就算，何妖堅持<br />\n同埋何妖係藍絲超高人氣<br />\n保皇怕新西立法會選舉𠝹死自己人"},{"pid":"34160d0fe608d17f798d58f644aebceffb07728f","tid":1916490,"uid":47042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:03:46.000Z","msg":"黎啦，愈多制度暴力就愈多人同意制度外抗爭<br />\n<br />\n睇下到時邊個奶野？"},{"pid":"ac37b3db698f570b95e4a4fdbbc42fb3d6e64123","tid":1916490,"uid":134997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34160d0fe608d17f798d58f644aebceffb07728f","tid":1916490,"uid":47042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:03:46.000Z","msg":"黎啦，愈多制度暴力就愈多人同意制度外抗爭<br />\n<br />\n睇下到時邊個奶野？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:05:34.000Z","msg":"港台會奶野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b0ebc555e0d9fef4a8c91b04da65121bf09ca1","tid":1916490,"uid":35456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:06:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b0e4d0736a60a2fcfdfba81fd8b038a567dbab5","tid":1916490,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:08:20.000Z","msg":"要分組點票，其他保皇狗唔會比位佢上，投棄權票多"},{"pid":"f9bdec58e7d5d1830b03e861135d7